    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302740/extras/44d7311e9c416e6b53334a704f3324db.poster.avif?t=1772117665\" width=806 height=454 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302740/extras/44d7311e9c416e6b53334a704f3324db.webm?t=1772117665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>这是一款敌人不可见的第一人称射击游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌人隐身——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能看到的只是他们投射出的影子。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302740/extras/f4d19db6e5aa6779c5fd9351b2297373.poster.avif?t=1772117665\" width=854 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302740/extras/f4d19db6e5aa6779c5fd9351b2297373.webm?t=1772117665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你只有一把枪，以及其他脆弱而短暂的光源：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >萤火虫、光球和烟花。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你每时每刻都得做出选择：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >先创造光影，还是先消灭敌人。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302740/extras/181e6ec8498a5acf8709dff689daa8b3.poster.avif?t=1772117665\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302740/extras/181e6ec8498a5acf8709dff689daa8b3.webm?t=1772117665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>游戏目标很简单——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>活下去，创造更多的光。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >极简系统，试图创造丰富的游戏体验。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302740/extras/63af1cc76c3519161ba4105844d10315.avif?t=1772117665\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302740/extras_big/63af1cc76c3519161ba4105844d10315.avif?t=1772117665 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >神说：「要有光」，于是便有了光。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >光不仅是装饰，也不只是氛围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >它是你发现敌人、塑造空间的武器。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302740/extras/89e155ddf176a3a711d5ddb9fb207880.avif?t=1772117665\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302740/extras_big/89e155ddf176a3a711d5ddb9fb207880.webp?t=1772117665 width=1560 height=878 /></span>光可以被追随、被操纵，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也可以被你创造。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一首用光与影写下的，关于建筑与记忆的游戏之诗。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302740/extras/a12ede85bdd80b7a8228ad60f1169741.avif?t=1772117665\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302740/extras_big/a12ede85bdd80b7a8228ad60f1169741.webp?t=1772117665 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌人隐身，只能通过影子显形</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >影子由你创造的光所产生</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单一枪械 + 多种光源武器构成的极简战斗系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有交互都源于基本的光影与物理碰撞，直观易上手</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >约十个相互独立的竞技场关卡，每一关都由玩家创造出，不同的光影与艺术可能性</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一位影逸杀手的表现，都将记录在Steam排行榜中</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你前所未见的，独特第一人称射击游戏体验</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※游戏中文界面即将上线</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※实机画面录像仅为体现玩法与氛围，实际难度可能有所调整。</p>",
